{"prompt": "Design a modern site for a digital marketing and SEO agency. The aesthetic should incorporate a bright cobalt blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Digital Marketing & SEO Agency</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff;\n            --secondary-color: #e6f2ff;\n            --text-color: #333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-bg: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            padding: 8px 15px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.8));\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .services, .about, .contact {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services h2, .about h2, .contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-items {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 280px;\n            max-width: 350px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-content img {\n            max-width: 40%;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .about-text h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact input,\n        .contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        .contact textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-bg);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Basic Font Awesome Integration (for icons) */\n        .fa {\n            display: inline-block;\n            font: normal normal normal 14px/1 FontAwesome;\n            font-size: inherit;\n            text-rendering: auto;\n            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n        }\n        .fa-rocket:before { content: \"\\f135\"; }\n        .fa-chart-line:before { content: \"\\f201\"; }\n        .fa-bullhorn:before { content: \"\\f026\"; }\n        .fa-lightbulb:before { content: \"\\f0eb\"; }\n        .fa-users:before { content: \"\\f0c0\"; }\n        .fa-envelope:before { content: \"\\f003\"; }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .services .service-items, .about-content {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            .about-content img {\n                max-width: 80%;\n                margin-bottom: 30px;\n            }\n            nav ul {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            nav ul li {\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Boost Your Brand Online</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Drive Growth with Data-Driven Digital Marketing</h2>\n            <p>We craft custom strategies to elevate your online presence, increase visibility, and achieve your business goals.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n     